    <string name="onboarding_step1_title">Install Termux</string>
    <string name="onboarding_step1_body">Hermes runs inside Termux. Install Termux from GitHub releases (not the Play Store). Open the Hermes tab to grant permissions and run the installer.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_step2_title">Grant permissions</string>
    <string name="onboarding_step2_body">LocalAgent needs POST notifications (for foreground work) and Termux “Run command” rights. If the system dialog fails, open Termux → App info → Permissions and allow LocalAgent.</string>
    <string name="onboarding_step3_title">API keys (optional)</string>
    <string name="onboarding_step3_body">Add cloud keys on the Keys tab or use one-tap local Qwen on the Local tab. Routing is explained in chat with /model.</string>
