    <string name="hermes_chatgpt_auth_title">ChatGPT / provider sign-in (Hermes)</string>
    <string name="hermes_chatgpt_auth_body">Desktop Hermes signs in through the CLI (device login, Codex import, etc.). LocalAgent’s Keys tab is for API keys merged into ~/.hermes/.env — it does not replace Hermes’s own auth store. After install, use this button so Termux runs hermes model interactively, same as on desktop.</string>
