    <string name="hermes_terminal_vs_termux_title">In-app Terminal vs Termux</string>
    <string name="hermes_terminal_vs_termux_body">This app’s Terminal tab runs /system/bin/sh with bridge env for debugging only. Real Hermes CLI runs inside Termux.</string>
    <string name="hermes_session_control_title">Stop / disconnect</string>
    <string name="hermes_session_control_body">Disconnect bridge closes active Hermes TCP sessions (they can reconnect). Stop Hermes runs killall inside Termux for the hermes binary only. For stuck installers or bash jobs, use Termux’s notification “Stop” or the Termux UI.</string>
